{"tid":1783201,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"貧窮人數創新高，資源應留給有需要人士，強烈要求削減警察福利","createTime":"2019-12-14T15:08:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-14T18:14:35.000Z","uid":36901,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"b1d18316004713253b368f0d2207c0a27d608856","tid":1783201,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T15:08:20.000Z","msg":"1.所有房屋福利取消，警察宿舍按市場價格出租或收回<br />\n<br />\n2.取消向警員及其家屬提供醫療及牙科福利<br />\n<br />\n3.有薪假期一律按勞工法律最低標準<br />\n<br />\n4.取消對警員及其子女的教育援助<br />\n<br />\n5.康樂及體育，收回各警察康樂會，俱樂部康樂設施用地，取消資助警員及其家屬入住酒店及渡假屋<br />\n<br />\n6.退休保障，mpf政府供款一律為法定最低標準，即2.5%，不得有任何特別供款。為確保警員退休生活，減少依賴政府福利，建議立法強制警察僱員供款至薪金30%，同時取消舊制長俸，有需要警員通過資產及入息審查後，可申請綜援。<br />\n<br />\n上述各項所節省的資源全數撥給區議會，以協助基層人士，騰出土地撥給區議會調配，協助無家可歸青年。"},{"pid":"94a4c84d9f4be23b988b878cd7bde246083bd982","tid":1783201,"uid":61277,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T15:09:59.000Z","msg":"根本應該成個狗隊budget cut左佢"},{"pid":"8b842b661f8766e314339631a7bee5e54c5f73ed","tid":1783201,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T15:11:21.000Z","msg":"一定要"},{"pid":"1008fdb1a4a4f0f2836f9b55c2ed68e7b55efb47","tid":1783201,"uid":62270,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T15:12:16.000Z","msg":"冇時間啦25號截止，極度要人幫手!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1782422\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1782422</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3cdf9a17aa80a613551a75296d8f2d1f99b9d143","tid":1783201,"uid":36901,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T15:12:58.000Z","msg":"公公婆婆<br />\n你知道嗎?<br />\n長者貧窮率高達30.9%，你份生果金連貧窮線都唔到<br />\n警察ot錢卻近10億公帑 ，夠起7間安老院!"},{"pid":"892f46ab41ce78ffe148cb9b3fc4cd0adc26f873","tid":1783201,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T15:18:28.000Z","msg":"各位基層工友，你知道嗎?<br />\n<br />\n當大家死做爛做先得個一萬幾千<br />\n出面開槍打人班popo份ot隨時多過你做兩個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e4ef1101b81637af2031b7f4c06385989e8e5aa","tid":1783201,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T15:19:54.000Z","msg":"弊在依班窮撚 好多都撐政府 撐黑狗呢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"950db1e8904f8ddf758142ac03879c84b1c4878b","tid":1783201,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T15:22:19.000Z","msg":"各位供樓人士<br />\n<br />\n當你死供爛供層，而popo一個唔該就可以走入你個屋苑拉人放tg<br />\n<br />\npopo自己卻居住無休<br />\n<br />\n警務人員房屋福利包括警察部門宿舍、公務員房屋福利及其他有關的房屋福利，包括：<br />\n<br />\n本地督察級宿舍<br />\n初級警務人員宿舍<br />\n為職位需要而設的宿舍<br />\n為行動需要而設的宿舍<br />\n公務員公屋配額<br />\n非實報實銷現金津貼<br />\n購屋貸款計劃<br />\n居所資助計劃"},{"pid":"d5ef489c2105a592ee25ed20577f29ec73075e92","tid":1783201,"uid":221125,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T15:23:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p6Zr5Ct.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp6Zr5Ct.jpg&h=299085e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jWFCsQQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjWFCsQQ.jpg&h=0e82254b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"13dc5e0964e0780e7dbabef0374996eb23f0bbcb","tid":1783201,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T15:25:54.000Z","msg":"各位輪緊公屋既朋友<br />\n<br />\n當你住劏房仲要食tg<br />\n<br />\n警務人員房屋福利卻多到嚇死你，包括：<br />\n<br />\n本地督察級宿舍<br />\n初級警務人員宿舍<br />\n為職位需要而設的宿舍<br />\n為行動需要而設的宿舍<br />\n公務員公屋配額<br />\n非實報實銷現金津貼<br />\n購屋貸款計劃<br />\n居所資助計劃<br />\n<br />\n警察薪高糧準有ot，房屋福利應留給有需要基層人士，認同請分享<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e86d1e53922d13b04bb497f418014b3394907ef","tid":1783201,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T15:33:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static01.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2280000/2283418/20190301_salary_600.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2280000%2F2283418%2F20190301_salary_600.png&h=401dd3dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n你知道嗎?<br />\n越受市民認同<br />\n人工越低"},{"pid":"9694ae874ca433151890233255d3118323f7a008","tid":1783201,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T15:38:43.000Z","msg":"你知道嗎?<br />\n特設大Sir會所 警猶如特權階級<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190924/60077092\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190924%2F60077092&d=WfKWFoUFzWEJR7ioTMJgWgbFtlMfP7wF5OAPhGI7yCY%3D&h=d9a4204e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190924%2F60077092&h=e16bc3f4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190924/60077092</a>"},{"pid":"1472525bb4dcbd9435dd4f2094c47475a5b8d57c","tid":1783201,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T15:42:44.000Z","msg":"你知道什麼是貧富懸殊嗎?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190718/large/1563428990_ea51.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190718%2Flarge%2F1563428990_ea51.jpg&h=446082ca&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"979610f7069231fef453f010b2e3327fd84b4aac","tid":1783201,"uid":87723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T15:43:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"568d0256ff20de3ac875536c78f534d83e3c161a","tid":1783201,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T15:45:59.000Z","msg":"退休保障，mpf政府供款一律為法定最低標準，<span style=\"color: red;\">即5%</span>，不得有任何特別供款。為確保警員退休生活，減少依賴政府福利，建議立法強制警察僱員供款至薪金30%，同時取消舊制長俸，有需要警員通過資產及入息審查後，可申請綜援"},{"pi